remarks: Membership in a closed interval and in a left open right closed interval.  (Contributed by Glauco Siliprandi, 11-Dec-2019.)
statement:
eliccelioc.a $e |- ( ph -> A e. RR ) $.
eliccelioc.b $e |- ( ph -> B e. RR ) $.
eliccelioc.c $e |- ( ph -> C e. RR* ) $.
eliccelioc $p |- ( ph -> ( C e. ( A (,] B ) <-> ( C e. ( A [,] B ) /\ C =/= A ) ) ) $.
